            <p class="view-details-faq"><span class="btn-plus btn-plus-faq"><span class="open">view details</span> <span class="close">Close</span> </span></p>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content accordion-content-faq" style="display: block;" data-accordion-id="faq-account" data-accordion-group="faq">
            <p>We use your Personal Data to:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>• process and complete orders you place via the Website;</li>
              <li>• process and deal with any complaints or inquiries made by you ;</li>
              <li>• monitor, develop and improve the Website and your experience when using the Website;</li>
              <li>• process the registration of your customer account and maintain your customer account;</li>
              <li>• send you dedicated offers and services; and</li>
              <li>• send you information and marketing materials about new or existing Lacoste products and services; and</li>
              <li>• recognize and reward top customers when applicable.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If you do not wish to receive marketing information from us, you can click on the relevant Unsubscribe button or email us at <a href="mailto:custserv@lacoste.com.ph">custserv@lacoste.com.ph</a>&nbsp;and let us know.</p>
            <br>
          </div>
          <div class="ordering-faq cgv-bg accordion accordion-faq active" data-accordion-href="faq-use" data-accordion-group="faq">
            <h2 class="block-title-faq">4. NEWSLETTERS</h2>
