          <div class="accordion-content accordion-content-faq" style="display: block;" data-accordion-id="faq-use" data-accordion-group="faq">
            <p>You can subscribe to the Lacoste newsletter and so choose to be informed at regular intervals of the commercial offers available on the website, at the Lacoste boutiques and those of our commercial partners.</p>
            <p>You have the opportunity at any time to unsubscribe by clicking on the link provided for this purpose at the end of each newsletter or by sending an email to <a href="mailto:custserv@lacoste.com.ph">custserv@lacoste.com.ph</a>.</p>
