          </div>
          <div class="ordering-faq cgv-bg accordion accordion-faq active" data-accordion-href="faq-delivery" data-accordion-group="faq">
            <h2 class="block-title-faq">5. HOW TO OPT IN OR OPT OUT FROM DIRECT MARKETING</h2>
