          <div class="ordering-faq cgv-bg accordion accordion-faq active" data-accordion-href="faq-delivery" data-accordion-group="faq">
            <h2 class="block-title-faq">6. PASSING ON YOUR PERSONAL DATA TO THIRD PARTIES</h2>
            <div class="spacer-faq-title">&nbsp;</div>
            <p class="view-details-faq"><span class="btn-plus btn-plus-faq"><span class="open">view details</span> <span class="close">Close</span> </span></p>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content accordion-content-faq" style="display: block;" data-accordion-id="faq-delivery" data-accordion-group="faq">
            <p>We may disclose your Personal Data to:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>• Any member of our group, which means our subsidiaries; our ultimate holding company; its subsidiaries; and certain of our business partners which help us in providing your order, delivering your goods, taking your payment and analysing your use of the website in order to improve the website's efficiency;</li>
              <li>• Other third parties which may use your personal data to send you information and marketing materials about their products and services. However, we will only pass your personal data on to such third parties if you have ticked an "opt-in" box to indicate that you wish to receive such information.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We may share, transfer or disclose your personal data to any potential or actual successor to our business.</p>
